title: BJP Divided Over Article 370?

BJP maybe making inroads in the Jammu and Kashmir but their party candidate has put them in a soup by raking up the Article 370 debate. Hina Bhat's comments are a direct contradiction to Prime Minister Narendra Modi's proposal of a debate on Article 370. The dissent in the BJP over the issue has given enough ammunition to the Congress to target the party. Social Media Links :-
